review_blob: Love this stuff,One of my all-time favorites.Very smooth,bitter malt,A+ .Great beer for the winter.
Take a coffee can,fill w/galvanized roofing nails,let sit out doors in water until they rust.Congratulations,youve brewed your very own 40 of ST. IDES
